<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> Aristotle, <i>Complete Works</i> (2 volumes), Princeton, 1995, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0691099502" class="internal">ISBN 0691099502</a></li>
